divs: Sighting DetailsI was in the parking lot and didn't hear any sound till it was right over head. it was a bar like objust that had a very loud sound but only when it was right over head. i saw it for about 1 or 2 seconds but after i saw it i could hear F18's being scrambled from Palm Springs International air port.it had alternating red and green lights but not the same colors as conventional aircraft there was no ACL lights on it and no whit lights. i was at work and my work is in the flight path of the airport so i know what aircraft look like at night. this was not a normal aircraft.
Summary: Bar Like about 120-200 feet off the ground
